---
title: Burrata with Zucchini 'Pappardelle' Sundried Tomato Pesto and Herby Ciabatta
description: Using raw zucchini as noodles, is a different way to enjoy this tasty vegetable! They are tossed in sun-dried tomato pesto and served with toasted garlic-ciabatta bread. Don't forget the best part, utterly delicious and super creamy Burrata!! Dinner tonight is simple and clean.
